1. Install pnpm
   - npm install -g pnpm
2. Create a React project using create-react-app.
   - pnpm create react-app project-name --template typescript
3. Delete node_modules, package-lock.json.
4 -1. Create a file ".npmrc"
  -2. add "auto-install-peers=true"
/* -3. remove node_modules               */
/* -4. reinstall packages (pnpm install) */
5. Install Packages using pnpm
   - pnpm install
6. Property 'toBeInTheDocument' does not exist on type 'JestMatchers<HTMLElement>'.
   - pnpm add -D @types/testing-library__jest-dom
7. // tsconfig.json
   {
     "compilerOptions": { ... },
     "exclude": ["node_modules", ".next"]
   }

* package.json ($npm_package_)
"scripts": {
  ...
  "add-extras": "pnpm add %npm_package_my_a_mui%"
  },
  "my": {
    "a: {
      "mui": "@mui/material @emotion/react @emotion/styled @fontsource/roboto @mui/icons-material"
    }
  },
